UI - Lifes counter, point counter, bullet counter (indicates when player will have to reload the gun)

Player needs to shoot enemies (spawning on the top of the screen) before they reach base (bottom of the screen).

Player will have to move contreoller around to aim, press the button, getting the feedback with the motor, to 
shoot and reload by pressign a button and pushing magazine upwards.

Parts required: Accelerometer/gyroscope, button, IR sensor, motor, arduino and other components to make it work.
